@startuml
left to right direction
actor "Codeforces API" as CF
rectangle "Codeforces gym sync" as P1
rectangle "Codeforces API adapter" as P2
rectangle "Codeforces HTTP client" as P3
database "class_gyms" as D1
database "teacher_codeforces_credentials" as D2
database "gym_problems" as D3
database "gym_standings" as D4
database "students/enrollments" as D5
P1 --> D1 : read bound gyms
P1 --> D2 : read teacher credentials
P1 --> P2 : list owned gyms / get snapshot
P2 --> P3 : API request
P3 --> CF : HTTP request
CF --> P3 : metadata/standings
P3 --> P2 : normalized response
P1 --> D1 : sync gym catalog
P1 --> D3 : sync problem list
P1 --> D5 : map handles to enrolled students
P1 --> D4 : sync gym standing rows
@enduml
